Note that the original by the artist pretty much straight-up uses the same dialogue as the panel. I just figured it'd be a nice touch to switch a couple of names here in addition of Alice.

Reference is, of course, [**Jujutsu Kaisen Ch.252**](https://mangadex.org/title/c52b2ce3-7f95-469c-96b0-479524fb7a1a/jujutsu-kaisen).
